4.0, child: CachedNetworkImage(imageUrl: imageUrl, fit: BoxFit.contain)))))))); } @override Widget build(BuildContext context) { return Hero(tag: heroTag, child: GestureDetector(onTap: () => _openFullScreen(context), child: ClipRRect(borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12), child: CachedNetworkImage(imageUrl: imageUrl, width: width, height: height, fit: BoxFit.cover, placeholder: (_, __) => Container(color: NiosPalette.surfaceHover, child: const Center(child: CircularProgressIndicator(strokeWidth: 2))), errorWidget: (_, __, ___) => Container(color: NiosPalette.surfaceHover, child: Icon(Icons.error_outline, color: NiosPalette.textSecondary)))))); } }
